{"tid":2201930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9.14 APM和你Lunch （Doris報導）","createTime":"2020-09-14T07:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:04:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e17b49f5ccaf59ae3474a0586151120939bdfcbc","tid":2201930,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"【直播】<br />\n9.14 APM和你Lunch<br />\n（Doris報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p2gmfePJfcQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp2gmfePJfcQ&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=381d3a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p2gmfePJfcQ</a><br />\n<br />\n《看中國》香港頻道<br />\n191K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n請支持袁先生發起的白宮請願，要求香港今年有真普選。香<br />\n1. 打開網頁 <br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/peti...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpeti...&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=d108edad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/peti...</a><br />\n1.a 也可以掃描QR Code。<br />\n2. 在網頁中間的右邊三長方格第一欄方格 &ldquo;First Name*&rdquo; 填寫你的名字<br />\n3. 第二欄方格 &ldquo;Last Name*&rdquo; 填寫你的姓氏<br />\n4. 第三欄方格 &ldquo;Email Address&rdquo; 填寫 &ldquo;電郵地址&rdquo; <br />\n5. 在綠色長方格 &ldquo;Sign Now&rdquo; 點按完成<br />\n6. 完成簽署後，會收到電郵通知要求確認簽署了此項請願，切記打開這份電郵，記得點擊 &ldquo;Confirm your signature by clicking here&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n再提大家簽署完後記得打開電郵回覆，必須要點擊&ldquo;Confirm your signature by clicking here&rdquo; 才算完成✅請願呀，多謝大家支持🙏🙏<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/peti...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpeti...&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=d108edad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/peti...</a><br />\n<br />\n立即加入《看中國》榮譽會員 <a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/kzgd/subs...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fkzgd%2Fsubs...&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=1d137025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/kzgd/subs...</a> <br />\n我哋係看中國駐香港嘅記者，過去一年，我哋每一日都奔走於抗爭街頭，頂住槍林彈雨、冒著催淚彈...<br />\n講真，我哋都會驚。但喺現場，香港人團結一致抵抗中共嘅意志和勇氣，俾咗我哋好大嘅鼓舞。今日，我哋越來越從容，喺呢塊曾經繁華無比嘅土地上，繼續奔走，用鏡頭呈現真實嘅香港俾您。<br />\n我哋唔單止報導香港嘅真實新聞，每年，亦有數以億計嘅中國人，透過我哋嘅網站睇到真實嘅中國同真實嘅世界。呢個係我哋無懼風雨前行嘅動力。但是我哋獨立報導嘅媒體渠道不斷受到Facebook、YouTube嘅審查、降級、甚至關閉。<br />\n加入榮譽會員，同我哋一起守護香港、守護14億中國人獲得真實訊息嘅權利。您的加入將有助我哋繼續前行。<br />\n<br />\n本視頻僅代表嘉賓或受訪者本人觀點。"},{"pid":"2455b2bec2bc556468c00622f76e5084cb9c7420","tid":2201930,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8a0c90b59b58001ce61585e361a2ac7fff8016","tid":2201930,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}